{"tid":1799669,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"（重要原則）想經濟攬炒，必須先紅後藍，否則只會事倍功半","createTime":"2019-12-27T06:28:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-28T06:43:13.000Z","uid":304769,"like":21,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"4c6f69c40b3136335ec344bad72fd5b98c52542a","tid":1799669,"uid":304769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T06:28:38.000Z","msg":"有人問我點解搞經濟攬炒，越搞恆指越升？我答佢：第一，股市同實質經濟不嬲都唔一致嘎啦，有時甚至可以背馳添。第二，就係香港股市係以中資為主，所以香港股市實際上不太代表香港。<br />\n因此，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>想經濟攬炒必須以打擊中資企業為主，尤其國企。請記住支共每賺到一分一毫，就多一分一毫整子彈殺手足。</strong></span><br />\n經濟攬炒target：<br />\n1.切斷中國國企在香港經營獲得外匯收入的機會，以加速支爆。<br />\n2.令藍絲企業經營困難，&ldquo;統戰&rdquo;綠絲企業<br />\n舉例，呢個原則點樣用：<br />\n基於先紅後藍原則，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">銀行方面一定係先中銀後匯豐</span></strong><br />\n基於先紅後藍原則，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>&ldquo;幫襯&rdquo;紅店力度不應該比藍店細。尤其各種隱性紅店係支共既重要回血劍</strong></span>。<br />\n記住，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>如果想經濟攬炒以及加速支爆，就要紅死藍貧，紅死是為了打擊支共呢個恐怖份子籌集資金。藍唔洗死，但要慘比其他綠絲睇，就係為左&ldquo;統戰&rdquo;綠絲，壯大黃色經濟圈。</strong></span>"},{"pid":"5db9246261065f348f724c60f204f89a3f71f25a","tid":1799669,"uid":263058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T06:29:08.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"af7be943b3c4684d1aec92dc2e041075813ec041","tid":1799669,"uid":191649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T06:30:16.000Z","msg":"統戰<br />\n<br />\n拉一派打一派<br />\n<br />\n阻止戰線太長"},{"pid":"66ec5045a11dca146ffde1729fb66a68a880aef1","tid":1799669,"uid":304769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"af7be943b3c4684d1aec92dc2e041075813ec041","tid":1799669,"uid":191649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T06:30:16.000Z","msg":"統戰<br />\n<br />\n拉一派打一派<br />\n<br />\n阻止戰線太長"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T06:33:52.000Z","msg":"exactly,雖然我唔想用蝗語，但係師以夷技以制夷，支共既&ldquo;統戰&rdquo;、&ldquo;拉一派打一派&rdquo;確實值得借鏡學習。"},{"pid":"4fbcb26b0d77c8be2f5ddf733dbf6bbde0b71cfd","tid":1799669,"uid":146030,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T06:49:49.000Z","msg":"所以唔好再搞美心同匯豐<br />\n一直唔知點解唔搞pacific coffee而要搞starbuck"},{"pid":"28b79e005ff2c245510a66f7aea1f294096655ad","tid":1799669,"uid":304769,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4fbcb26b0d77c8be2f5ddf733dbf6bbde0b71cfd","tid":1799669,"uid":146030,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T06:49:49.000Z","msg":"所以唔好再搞美心同匯豐<br />\n一直唔知點解唔搞pacific coffee而要搞starbuck"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T06:55:07.000Z","msg":"exactly，根據先紅後藍原則，應該先Pacific(華潤)後Starbucks（美心）"},{"pid":"e0433bbe8144a84d12cdbb57be18fcf5117e873c","tid":1799669,"uid":211034,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T08:21:36.000Z","msg":"同意一定係先紅後藍<br />\n先中銀後匯豐, 先Pacific Coffee後starbucks"},{"pid":"c1037b4a664b523782f78d3f99ba95f8ce9c5759","tid":1799669,"uid":211034,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T08:21:49.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ea3b704d8ee936e3145cc134a58a392658df7f2e","tid":1799669,"uid":15362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T08:23:33.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"f24bd087b2a3c36d523ebe7fd258ecb5ef1b378f","tid":1799669,"uid":28004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T08:24:43.000Z","msg":"冇用，連登仔只會話佢地背叛香港人，仲衰過中資本身<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9609d3f02cbf72482df3b7983fa47e65200b0f8","tid":1799669,"uid":292710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f24bd087b2a3c36d523ebe7fd258ecb5ef1b378f","tid":1799669,"uid":28004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T08:24:43.000Z","msg":"冇用，連登仔只會話佢地背叛香港人，仲衰過中資本身<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T08:28:17.000Z","msg":"咁咪出事囉"},{"pid":"0e218a3fbd8973748c6c0caf14d1f9699993e316","tid":1799669,"uid":304769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f24bd087b2a3c36d523ebe7fd258ecb5ef1b378f","tid":1799669,"uid":28004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T08:24:43.000Z","msg":"冇用，連登仔只會話佢地背叛香港人，仲衰過中資本身<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T08:34:48.000Z","msg":"呢個就係管理學，stakeholder engagement 當中要考慮power同interest既問題。藍店係叛逃，確實更令人討厭，因為佢地係自願選擇同我地敵對（高interest），但係佢地無咩實力，頂多得把口鬧人曱甴(低power)。<br />\n相反，中資國企雖然身不由己站在敵陣（低interest），但係佢地背後係中共，大把資源，係推惡法、推警暴、滅香港既主腦（高power）。<br />\n所以，我建議先紅後黑，等支爆左，香港光復左再慢慢清算藍絲都唔遲。"},{"pid":"cc05a532df788ca933dcb51d4f4f3d717d4f3655","tid":1799669,"uid":304769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T08:54:22.000Z","msg":"無言負評開始出現，說明五毛來了，多謝五毛認證我既想法<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07d8c510b1570e5b196e3059ddfaf8b2c0748057","tid":1799669,"uid":301152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T09:07:49.000Z","msg":"華潤集團<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZOEagqo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZOEagqo.jpg&h=decd12d0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"416e42a637dde77fb223f168e65418c9afdac87e","tid":1799669,"uid":164752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T12:30:52.000Z","msg":"認同"},{"pid":"a1f2df0ec902a2bb0f114c50048cc79b6d8cf787","tid":1799669,"uid":164752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T12:39:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d5eeb26f1447c41f8183346e347971d778e8564","tid":1799669,"uid":164752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"07d8c510b1570e5b196e3059ddfaf8b2c0748057","tid":1799669,"uid":301152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T09:07:49.000Z","msg":"華潤集團<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZOEagqo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZOEagqo.jpg&h=decd12